{"tid":1438131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請所有弟兄姊妹注意","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T17:03:03.000Z","uid":197782,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"963296947be918525d857afbe288be77c5c23777","tid":1438131,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:45:08.000Z","msg":"經歷咗兩個月咁多件事，大家都開始攰係正常。<br />\n但係請唔好忘記我香港人咁鋪係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔輸得</span></span>！<br />\n有手足為咗香港而犧牲！<br />\n有後生為咗香港失前途！<br />\n亦有人為香港冇咗頭家！<br />\n請記住，我地冇贏！<br />\n我地都未成功爭取！<br />\n宜家事勢不停變，但我地面對藍絲並冇屈服。<br />\n面對暴力，我地唔害怕。<br />\n面對強權，我地更勇敢。<br />\n但我地怕內鬥，怕唔再敢信自己人。<br />\n所以！<br />\n請記得五大訴求。<br />\n同時，不分化，不割蓆。<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做。<br />\n可能有手足嘅行為你認為唔恰當，但請唔好譴責。<br />\n勇武護和理，和理撐勇武。<br />\n咁先係香港人嘅革命！<br />\n利申：近期見有人有分歧，實在不忍眼見弟兄之爭故有感而發。"},{"pid":"55d82762c34cc5c17dee9aeac939f00fd5880312","tid":1438131,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d5274822f1a4f918946f9664b04cf6578ab8ce","tid":1438131,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ff4371271bafae5d97c3deff1403300161795d","tid":1438131,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d69554fb4b571de68d0387be7e1594491d28d82","tid":1438131,"uid":96964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:07.000Z","msg":"一輸就會清算"},{"pid":"0d3879796cef657e8092229208c981e7a3d7112e","tid":1438131,"uid":287508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a83002b0cfc1896dd7534e37d2eed69a4c44bf71","tid":1438131,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d